title: Bobby's Proposition For Collin Raye + Someone Opting Out Of Raymundo’s Wedding + Bobby Assigns Security Code Names

Bobby talks about listening to Collin Raye’s music and being surprised that his favorite song wasn’t his most streamed song. Someone on the shows asks if they can opt out and not be a part of Raymundo’s wedding. Plus, Bobby gives each member of the show a security code name!
